Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.75,0:00:07.10,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,这场恋爱令人战栗，震惊，焦虑难耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.35,0:00:10.70,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,受不可名状的力量驱使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.80,0:00:18.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,来势汹涌让人无法禁闭心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.30,0:00:36.25,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我们感受得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.80,0:00:46.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,爱情的利刺或许同样加之于你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.00,0:00:53.40,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,不知你究竟为何心痛 为何胆怯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.55,0:00:58.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕去面对纠葛不清的二人真实面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.10,0:01:01.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,生怕面对彼此的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.35,0:01:06.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,这场恋爱令人战栗，震惊，焦虑难耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.00,0:01:14.15,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,即使迷茫想时似乎随着清风而逝 仍然无法抱个满怀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.25,0:01:17.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在我小小的胸臆中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.75,0:01:21.22,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,无法紧闭心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.32,0:01:25.75,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,深藏着朝着下一步迈进的惶惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.80,0:01:35.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,500)}即使我已将迷惑拥个满怀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.70,0:22:36.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,透过窗户看到天空 描绘着飞机留下的云迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.90,0:22:45.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,净是回想今天和你争吵的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.80,0:22:55.95,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,琐碎的事情弄得束手无策 坐立不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.95,0:23:00.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,不自然地马上给你打电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.60,0:23:04.10,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,还是喜欢看到你迷人的笑脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.50,0:23:09.45,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,非常幸福的时光将要来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.55,0:23:14.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,伴随着痛苦的脚步声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.70,0:23:23.45,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,过于多心反而陷入更深的困境 然而却又守侯在你的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.50,0:23:32.40,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,夏之幻想 合上双眼最先浮现眼前的还是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.90,0:23:36.70,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,别无所求 只想和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.80,0:23:41.95,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就算束手无策也愿意 紧牵的手永不放开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.80,0:00:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坚强的内心蕴含着推理的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.50,0:00:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远以最强劲的节奏揭开事件的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去总是很严肃的警察们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.80,0:00:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也会为了事件与爱情而奋斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.90,0:00:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.10,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来…乖小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.80,0:02:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长大 不停地长大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烧得更猛烈一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.00,0:02:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的罪恶燃烧起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.10,0:02:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还需要一根火柴 还要一根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.20,0:02:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能结束一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.70,0:02:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随后这红色的火焰便会烧掉整个东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.80,0:03:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使一切重新开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.20,0:03:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.70,0:03:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.90,0:03:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走 回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.10,0:03:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.80,0:03:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本厅的刑事恋爱物语3（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警视厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.40,0:03:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的眼睛什么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.10,0:03:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.40,0:03:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛像狐狸一样往上吊 就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛往上吊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是像这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你画得好难看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全像是小孩子在涂鸦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有其他画的比较好的人了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,画师的妈妈今天感冒 他请了假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.20,0:04:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确是呢 佐藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.80,0:04:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.10,0:04:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种画怎么也无法交给搜查人员啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.10,0:04:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然线条利落 画风耐人寻味 但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.30,0:04:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你们来画得可爱点让我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个 画画嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我擅长的是印象画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.40,0:04:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等…白鸟 差劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.40,0:04:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这个人其实也未必是纵火犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.50,0:04:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你是说步美在说谎吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别把小孩子当傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.00,0:05:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她又没有亲眼看到那个男人纵火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.10,0:05:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天气这么热 那个人还穿着长大衣 带着手套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.00,0:05:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裤子上还有被汽油泼到的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.70,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还带着诡异的笑容出现在纵火现场的街道中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的人如果不是纵火犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是太说不过去了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.00,0:05:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吧 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.10,0:05:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.10,0:05:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之 大家一起去犯罪现场看看怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去（太好了）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.80,0:05:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开车送你们去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.50,0:05:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 我要顺道绕到别的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚好顺路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到别处去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天对我而言是一个特别的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特…特别的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤的生日吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.20,0:06:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.00,0:06:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要去哪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.20,0:06:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特别的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.00,0:06:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是佐藤父亲佐藤正义警官的祭日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.20,0:06:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是他的殉职日了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.70,0:06:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好是十八年前的今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在追捕银行抢匪途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个咖啡店这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.50,0:06:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这咖啡店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.40,0:07:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.60,0:07:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个咖啡店门口被大卡车撞倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.90,0:07:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不幸的是天下着大雨 救护车来得太迟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.80,0:07:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官是躺在救护车上在家人的陪伴下断气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警部那里听来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件案子的名字好象是叫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.70,0:07:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愁思郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.70,0:07:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 愁思郎 就是愁思郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.60,0:07:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于被卡车撞倒的警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.90,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不断地对逃走的犯人叫着这个谜样的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.80,0:07:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才被命名为愁思郎事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.20,0:07:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时警察还展开了大规模的搜查网
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.80,0:07:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是因为掌握核心事件的警官已经过世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以侦查行动便停顿下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三年前这件事已经过了追诉时效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我是听小五郎叔叔说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个事件我知道 在电视上看到过好几次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.70,0:08:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.70,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一项计划周密的犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的线索只有银行监视器拍摄下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不到十秒钟的画面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.80,0:08:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不知道已经殉职的警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.10,0:08:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是根据何种方法锁定嫌疑犯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个事件就在重重迷雾中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但万万没想到那位警官竟然就是佐藤的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.40,0:08:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们往往只记住案犯姓名和犯罪经过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁又会记得案件中殉职的警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.10,0:08:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非是警察或者别的有关人士才会记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐…佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.20,0:08:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们工作并不是为了让大家记住我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.20,0:08:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可当时那个卡车司机没有看到犯人的脸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.10,0:09:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 犯人好象当时穿着长长的雨披
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.40,0:09:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此是男是女都分辨不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且银行监视器拍到的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴着帽子 太阳眼镜和口罩 穿着大衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.80,0:09:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经知道犯人的名字叫“愁思郎”了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.50,0:09:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有任何一个叫这个名字的人有涉案的嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.40,0:09:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难怪整个案件就像是在重重迷雾中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.70,0:09:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,线索只有监视器拍到的画面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿着雨衣的犯人身影和“愁思郎”这三个字而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有四条线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四条线索是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.20,0:09:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲写在警察手册上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.30,0:09:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三个奇怪的片假名 カンオ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,カンオ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是第一次听到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.30,0:09:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方似乎没透露这件事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.60,0:09:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为其它警察都没听父亲说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但从父亲前后的记述来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有密切的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且当时我记得我跟我妈还被问了好几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然…然后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.70,0:10:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一次都没听说过 而且根本不明白其涵义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.20,0:10:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我小时候曾盯着这三个字很用心地想过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.50,0:10:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果谁能帮我解开这个谜 把愁思郎给逮捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.30,0:10:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意为他做任何事 达成他的所有愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.30,0:10:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 任何…要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.70,0:10:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要一千份鳗鱼饭可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.90,0:10:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.10,0:10:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去多罗碧加乐园看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.20,0:10:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要国际宇宙车站的车票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.50,0:10:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 会要个PRADA的名牌皮包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.30,0:10:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以要这届世界杯足球赛的入场券吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.00,0:10:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这帮小孩子真是现实得恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.70,0:10:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你们两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.10,0:10:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.80,0:11:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是美和子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你长大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.20,0:11:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是爸爸高中时代的棒球队的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.70,0:11:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我爸爸的最佳拍档 投手猿渡秀朗先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.50,0:11:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.30,0:11:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以臂力强脚程快著称的鹿野修二先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.90,0:11:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,值得信赖的第四棒猪保满雄先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.30,0:11:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有美丽的球队经理神鸟蝶子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.50,0:11:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别笑话我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已经是五十岁的老太婆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家都怎么会在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.90,0:11:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好久没见 想聚聚喝上一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.20,0:11:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前跟佐藤队长打个招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一起来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.00,0:11:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果以前没有邀请他 他都会生气呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.10,0:12:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（我们还是在那家居酒屋）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是白鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（你工作结束后也来坐坐吧）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.00,0:12:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 目暮警部 现在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.40,0:12:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在在杯户町第四条街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人发现像纵火犯的可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.90,0:12:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 地点就走品川的第六条街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.20,0:12:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个男人在临检的时候突然逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前正在追捕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.80,0:12:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的特征是长发 戴帽子 穿着灰色的长大衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.70,0:12:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,位置离你们很近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子就托佐藤看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.60,0:12:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和高木立刻赶往现场支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.80,0:12:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 快上车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察证…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.20,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手枪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.90,0:12:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.70,0:13:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手铐 手铐放在一科的桌子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.10,0:13:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间回去拿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧 高木君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.60,0:13:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.90,0:13:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万一有状况 还有白鸟警官的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我看过杂志上的占星专栏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.80,0:13:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天可是超级幸运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.80,0:13:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有带手铐也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正只是一个纵火犯而已嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公 小心些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.10,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,占卜的说我今天会很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.40,0:13:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 爸爸忘了带手铐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.60,0:13:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我先生 被车撞倒了 现在在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…为什么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.60,0:13:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸明明是站在正义一方的 你为正义而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.10,0:14:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 所谓正义就是…就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.50,0:14:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 佐藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.40,0:14:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 请等一下 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.70,0:14:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.80,0:14:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.90,0:14:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经生锈了呢 这个手铐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没带手铐就带上这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我爸爸的遗物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.20,0:14:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的手铐不是在东田先生的那次事件当中弄坏了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.60,0:14:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我暂时就先用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正好给你当护身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.10,0:15:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,护身符 你父亲不是因公殉职了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.00,0:15:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 那么小心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.70,0:15:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤  （高木）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.70,0:15:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.10,0:15:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 去逮捕纵火犯还需要携带手枪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.70,0:15:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 差遣高木警官他们的是刑事案侦察科
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与纵火犯有什么关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为发现被刺杀的尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在第四件纵火案现场附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然无确凿证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过可能死者因为目击歹徒纵火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.40,0:15:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是要加以制止才遭到杀害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们出动就是因为这个原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.40,0:15:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们千万别离开我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.40,0:15:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.10,0:16:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,品川站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警部 我是白鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经到了品川车站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把逃跑中的嫌疑犯逮捕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.90,0:16:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.00,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可当事人并不承认他是纵火犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是一个闯空门的小偷而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.60,0:16:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.30,0:16:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谜底揭晓了 我今天果然运气奇佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 佐藤警官的电话是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.70,0:16:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.90,0:16:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.70,0:16:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.20,0:16:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 你要给谁打电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.90,0:16:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有 我去趟洗手间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我转这个假面超人玩具机的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然有一个奇怪的叔叔从那里出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.00,0:17:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是佐藤 啊 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么新进展吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.80,0:17:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你知道十八年前的凶手是谁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.80,0:17:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 根据我的推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.60,0:17:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听了可不要吓一跳哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.60,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人可能是我们今天上午见过的那四个人当中的某个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊 白鸟警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.90,0:17:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 今天你的行动很可疑哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.80,0:17:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没呢 完全没有的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.40,0:18:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我全明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.20,0:18:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愁思郎的真正涵义“カンオ”之谜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.20,0:18:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你的父亲能锁定犯人的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彻头彻尾地明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.30,0:18:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过时效毕竟已过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.80,0:18:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢…犯人究竟是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.40,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.00,0:18:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 高木 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.10,0:18:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 高木 你怎么了 快回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 快回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.80,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.00,0:19:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.60,0:19:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是白鸟 啊 佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.80,0:19:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚好把疑犯送到品川警局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 高木吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.60,0:19:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 值勤时还在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.50,0:19:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你快把最后看到他的时间和地点告诉总厅指挥部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木被人偷袭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才跟我通话时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.10,0:19:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方很有可能是那个纵火犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要小心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是高木警官是在电话里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.30,0:19:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要说出十八年前的犯人的时候被偷袭的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不是表示…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.90,0:20:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个事件三年前就过时效了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.80,0:20:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不知道他说的是不是正确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在傍晚遇到的那四个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说要去居酒屋喝酒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地点在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.70,0:20:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.60,0:20:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家店叫做七曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.10,0:20:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地点在品川车站前面的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.30,0:20:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果像刚才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.50,0:20:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官在电话里所说的犯人就在那四个人当中的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人可能和高木警官同在车站前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶然听到了高木警官的谈话内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.30,0:20:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是攻击高木警官 企图灭口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是很有可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.20,0:20:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之 我去下品川车站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.40,0:20:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家先搭电车回家 明天到总厅去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.40,0:21:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,袭击高木刑警的人也可能是纵火犯不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.90,0:21:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你不是应该带上唯一的目击证人步美去才对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.30,0:21:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.90,0:21:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.70,0:21:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警视厅呼叫各分局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.30,0:21:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及品川境内的调查人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案发地点在品川车站附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.00,0:21:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,详细情况仍不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.60,0:21:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过若发现一名警察被人殴打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.20,0:21:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请立刻通知本厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.20,0:21:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再重复一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.20,0:21:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警视厅呼叫各分局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.80,0:21:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及品川境内的调查人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.50,0:21:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案发地点在品川车站附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假的 这不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.30,0:21:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那四个人当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.20,0:22:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀死我爸爸的凶手居然在那四个人当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.40,0:22:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.60,0:23:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人 那个人就是我看到的坏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.90,0:23:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不见了 那几个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.00,0:23:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样看得到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.90,0:24:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 难道说 袭击高木的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.70,0:24:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.70,0:24:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 我们俩一起喝一杯庆祝庆祝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,カンオ先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.90,0:24:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.30,0:24:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本厅刑事的恋爱故事3(后篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.80,0:24:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.50,0:24:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗马字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.40,0:24:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回是解决篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.70,0:24:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是高木 精神饱满中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.90,0:24:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.10,0:24:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了…哦哦
